name: Batenburgs
overview:
It always gets difficult when it comes to choosing a unique gift for your loved ones. Well, Batenburgs helps you in creating customized gift baskets and getting it delivered in Auckland and NZ wide.

They provide you with affordable gourmet hampers and corporate gifts for any occasion. If it is an alcohol gift hamper that you are after then Batenburgs can get you exactly what you want. You can get Jack Daniels to wine or just get a 100% Kiwi basket which will include wines that are exclusively made in New Zealand and loved by New Zealand people.

Why are the gift baskets at Batenburgs unique? The reason is simple. It is because they make gift baskets as per your preference, so you have the option to add things that you want and deduct things that you don’t want. Include anything that is close to you and express your feelings truly. Gifts are one way of expressing of your feelings for your loved ones and if you can’t get the right gift then you are missing out on expressing your feelings.
